  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd   \u0b87\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The person who posted against the politician is suspended",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A teacher has been suspended from service for uploading a rant against a Badulai regional politician on his Facebook.",
        "Due to the complaint made by the concerned politician at the police station against the said teacher, a case has also been filed against the teacher in the Badulai Magistrate Court.",
        "Meanwhile, Sri Lanka Teachers Union Secretary Joseph Stalin said that the suspension of the said teacher's service is illegal.",
        "Based on a political background, the teacher's service has been suspended. He also said that trade union activities will be carried out soon against this action."
      ],
